text: Mohamed El-Saharty (born 26 July 1990) is an Egyptian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Egypt Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Giza
